title: Responsible AI Product Management
description: Guest panelist for UW Foster School of Business AI Product Management class alongside Orlando Lugo of Salesforce. Discussed responsible AI efforts in government and industry, AI governance approaches, and the importance of principles over hype in AI development.

title: Staying Relevant in a Changing Analytics World
description: Career retrospective talk for Dr. Kanad Basu's Data Mining for Business Analytics class at GMU, focusing on why soft skills matter more than ever as AI capabilities are evolving rapidly.

title: AI and Cybersecurity Presentation
description: Presentation for Basha High School students exploring the intersection of artificial intelligence and cybersecurity, covering threats, opportunities, and practical ways to get started with AI.
